  "title": "Director of Communications",
  "description": "<p>· Develop, refine, and maintain the Fund’s overall branding strategy, ensuring clarity, consistency, and alignment across all internal and external communication channels.</p>\n<p>· Provide post-investment marketing support to portfolio companies, including narrative development, content planning, messaging refinement, and brand amplification initiatives.</p>\n<p>· Manage and coordinate all media-related activities for the Fund, including interviews, press releases, media statements, and securing coverage opportunities with key industry publications and outlets.</p>\n<p>· Provide ongoing strategic advice on market positioning, industry trends, and communication tactics for both the Fund and its portfolio companies, including proactive recommendations to strengthen public perception and competitive positioning.</p>\n<p>· Assist in the planning, execution, and management of marketing campaigns, events, ecosystem initiatives, and other visibility-enhancing activities undertaken by the Fund.</p>",
